.TH "acpi_dma_simple_xlate" 9 "acpi_dma_simple_xlate" "May 2021" "Kernel Hacker's Manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
acpi_dma_simple_xlate \- Simple ACPI DMA engine translation helper
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "struct dma_chan *" acpi_dma_simple_xlate
.BI "(struct acpi_dma_spec *dma_spec "  ","
.BI "struct acpi_dma *adma "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "dma_spec" 12
pointer to ACPI DMA specifier
.IP "adma" 12
pointer to ACPI DMA controller data
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
A simple translation function for ACPI based devices. Passes \fIstruct
dma_spec\fP to the DMA controller driver provided filter function.
.SH "RETURN"
Pointer to the channel if found or NULL otherwise.
